</td>
<td id="BBFB44949F1BDAB2E5135CB618945321" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" rowspan="1">Median vittae not obvious; lateral vittae with stripe pigmentation</td>
<td id="AA8E0941E76A5194012284CCBF2D8817" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" rowspan="1">Anal point straight and parallel-sided</td>
<td id="19819B054198B142683747BEB07C2806" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" rowspan="1">With dark annulus on femur of P2 and P3</td>
</tr>
<tr id="0B3A1EC02AF6794C3DBCD97F83064AC3" pageId="0" pageNumber="93">
<td id="38CD68D25FAF2E03A3817EEF11A87992" colspan="1" pageId="0" pageNumber="93" rowspan="1">
